Resource Profile: Patient-Generated Health Data Provenance

Official URL: https://2rdoc.pt/ig/ios-lifestyle-medicine/StructureDefinition/pghd-provenance Version: 0.1.0
Active as of 2025-11-27 Computable Name: PGHDProvenance

Provenance profile for tracking the origin and transformation history of PGHD from wearable devices

Usos:

  • Exemplos para este Perfil: Provenance/ProvenanceDetailedCaptureExample, Provenance/ProvenanceDeviceCaptureExample, Provenance/ProvenanceTransformationExample and Provenance/ProvenanceTransmissionExample

You can also check for usages in the FHIR IG Statistics
